{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@"},{"kind":"attribute","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","text":"MainActor"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSCheckbox"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"mentions":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Controls"],"kind":"mentions"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"Indicator states","type":"heading","anchor":"Indicator-states"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This checkbox indicator has two available states:","type":"text"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"selected"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": the checkbox is filled with a tick, the user has made the action to select the checkbox"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"unselected","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": the checkbox is empty, does not contain a tick, the user has made the action to unselect or did not select yet the checkbox","type":"text"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If you need to use a tri-state checkbox instead, refer to ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"text":"Particular cases","type":"heading","anchor":"Particular-cases"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckbox","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"A dedicated look-and-feel is implemented for that if the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"isError"},{"type":"text","text":" flag is risen."}]},{"level":2,"text":"Accessibility considerations","type":"heading","anchor":"Accessibility-considerations"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note also the component must be instanciated with a string parameter used as accessibility label."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It is a good pratice (at least) to define a label for a component without text for accessibility reasons. This label will be vocalized by "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Voice Over"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The vocalization tool will also use, after the label, a description of the component (if disabled, if error context), and a fake trait for checkbox."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"No accessibility identifier is defined in OUDS side as this value remains in the users hands.","type":"text"}]},{"level":2,"text":"Cases forbidden by design","type":"heading","anchor":"Cases-forbidden-by-design"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error or a read only situation and a disabled component.","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"}]},{"level":2,"text":"Code samples","type":"heading","anchor":"Code-samples"},{"type":"codeListing","code":["    \/\/ Supposing we have a selected checkbox","    @Published var isOn: Bool = true","","    \/\/ A simple checkbox, no error, not in read only mode","    OUDSCheckbox(isOn: $isOn, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\")","","    \/\/ A simple checkbox, but is an error context","    OUDSCheckbox(isOn: $isOn, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\"), isError: true)","","    \/\/ Never disable an error-related checkbox as it will crash","    \/\/ This is forbidden by design!","    OUDSCheckbox(isOn: $isOn, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\"), isError: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal e